These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, lemonade, mirinda, water
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, soul, punk, jazz
1. the fan hip-hop is somewhere to the left of the fan punk##5
2. the person drinking lemonade is not the fan hip-hop##6
3. the fan hip-hop is on the right of the fan jazz##1
4. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the fan punk##1
5. the person drinking juice is on the right of the fan hip-hop##1
6. the fan hip-hop is not the person drinking mirinda##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | lemonade   | water    | juice    | mirinda |
| Sport      | jazz | hip-hop | punk | soul |

