.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, rose, daffodil, balloon-flower
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, grapefruit, lettuce, onion
1. the person eating artichoke is on the far right##1
2. the person who growsrose is somewhere to the left of the person who growsdaffodil##5
3. the person eating onion is somewhere to the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##5
4. the person who growsrose is not the person eating grapefruit##6
5. the person eating onion is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
6. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
7. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
8. the person who growsdaffodil is somewhere to the left of the person who growsmarigold##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | rose  | daffodil    | marigold | balloon-flower    |
| Food       | onion | grapefruit | lettuce  | artichoke |

