.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, sprite, water
There are 4 different favourite colors: ebony, black, ivory, grey
1. the person drinking water is not the person who likes ebony##6
2. the person who likes black is not the person drinking sprite##6
3. the person who likes ivory is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
4. the person who likes black is the person drinking fanta##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person who likes black##1
6. the person drinking fanta is in an odd position##4
7. the person who likes ebony is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who likes ivory is somewhere to the left of the person who likes grey##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | water       | hot-chocolate  | fanta  | sprite |
| Job        | ivory | grey | black | ebony  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-4::.
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, guinea-pig, hedgehog, snake
There 4 different types of food: onion, grapefruit, peas, apple
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the left of the person eating onion##5
3. the person eating apple is not the owner of the guinea-pig##6
4. the person eating apple is somewhere to the right of the person eating onion##5
5. the person eating peas is on the right of the person eating grapefruit##1
6. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the left of the person eating apple##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |    4     |
| Pet         | guinea-pig | hedgehog | snake     | goldfish |
| Transport   | grapefruit     | peas    | onion | apple    |

