.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, iced-tea, milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbingd-games, singing, rock-climbing, dancing
1. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
2. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##5
3. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is singing##5
4. the person drinking fanta is not the person who's hobby is dancing##6
5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbingd-games is not the person drinking 7up##6
6. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | 7up        | milk | iced-tea | fanta |
| Transport   | dancing | rock-climbingd-games | singing     | rock-climbing   |

