2. the person watching thriller movies is not the person who growspoppy##6
3. the person who growsbegonia is on the far right##1
4. the person who growspoppy is somewhere to the right of the person who growsdaffodil##5
5. the person watching spy movies is the person watching spy movies##1
6. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the left of the person who growsbegonia##5
7. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching disaster movies##5
8. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere to the left of the person who growsdaffodil##5
9. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere to the left of the person who growsdaffodil##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | spy    | disaster  | thriller   |
| Nationality   | sunflower  | daffodil | poppy | begonia |

