5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person playing scrabble##3
6. the person playing chess is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
7. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##5
8. the person drinking milk is not the person playing mah-jongg##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |       3       |      4       |
