2. the person driving the helicopter is not the person watching western movies##6
3. the person driving the airplane is somewhere to the right of the person watching comedy movies##5
4. the person driving the subway is in an even position##4
5. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
6. the person driving the subway is the person watching comedy movies##1
7. the person watching musical movies is not the person driving the subway##6
8. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching western movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Job         | musical  | comedy | western    | martial-arts |
| Transport   | helicopter | subway | skateboard | airplane  |

