2. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
4. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
5. the person playing billiard is not the person who's sport is weightlifting##6
6. the person who's sport is surfing is not the person playing monopoly##6
7. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an even position##4
8. the person playing billiard is the person who's sport is golf##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4     |
| Pet     | billiard | go        | snooker  | monopoly     |
| Sport   | golf     | weightlifting | surfing | swimming |

