4. the person drinking lemonade is between the fan pop and the person drinking coffee##2
5. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
6. the fan electronic is between the fan disco and the person drinking cola##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |   3   |     4     |
