1. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the right of the person drinking coffee##5
2. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
4. the person drinking fanta is not the person who's hobby is board-games##6
5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the person who's hobby is board-games and the person who's hobby is singing##2
6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
8. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | singing | skydiving | board-games | woodworking |
| Pet     | coffee  | almond-milk      | soy-milk  | fanta       |

